<greg-page-template>
  <first-content>
    <ng-container *ngIf="areEnteringTreasure$ | async; else rollingTreasure">
      <greg-treasure-form></greg-treasure-form>
    </ng-container>
    <ng-template #rollingTreasure>
      <greg-roll-treasure></greg-roll-treasure>
    </ng-template>
  </first-content>
  <second-content>
    <greg-treasure-list></greg-treasure-list>
  </second-content>
</greg-page-template>
import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core';

@Component({
  selector: 'greg-enter-treasure',
  templateUrl: './enter-treasure.component.html',
  styleUrls: ['./enter-treasure.component.scss']
})
export class EnterTreasureComponent implements OnInit {

  constructor() { }

  ngOnInit(): void {
  }

}
